Span.Text: Track offenders throughout the entire criminal justice lifecycle.  Access offender data from anywhere and visit more offenders, more frequently with virtual monitoring solutions.  Speed up collaboration, reduce duplication, and streamline the distribution of case management or prisoner information within and between different agencies—police, prosecution, courts, and prison and parole organisations, by converting paper-based processes to automated workflows.
Instant access to location, people and evidence information makes it easy to get a complete view of an offender crime.
A map view provides instant visual access to your location and the incidents around you.  You can drill into any incident to find out more information.
